HEADWORD: Woodcraft
<hw>Wood"craft`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Skill and practice
in anything pertaining to the woods, especially in shooting, and other
sports in the woods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men of the glade and forest! leave⟦br⟧
Your <qex>woodcraft</qex> for the field of fight.</q>
<rj><qau>Bryant.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

